{
  "stem": "4710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you give away a whole bread?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- it's overpaid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was two and a half years older than me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, sister, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know anything about my sister, because-- because the other day, when we arrived in Auschwitz, she went in the-- in the women's camp, and that was the last we heard of her.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, what we-- first, we knew about her [INAUDIBLE] after the war, when we found out that she is in Germany, and soon we will-- we will-- she will be back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember there were a lot of-- lot of little incidents which I don't remember clearly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] No, I don't think-- I don't think it just comes to me anything else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I should have-- should have prepared myself better for the interview, I--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were evacuated, it was-- it was early morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said we are going to be evacuated, and we had to stand up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But everybody had to-- had to stand up in rounds of five.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just you see that-- that-- that the beginning of the [INAUDIBLE] is already out of the gates of the camp, and we're just following it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was quite-- quite in a rush.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we just walked, kept on walking, accompanied-- accompanied by Wehrmacht soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Possibly, they couldn't spare the SS by then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we walked for-- for almost 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was very hard for me, because-- because I just came out from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Besides, even if I would have been my normal strength, but being in hospital, when you had no-- no chance of walking or exercise.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And your body gets a bit flabby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after-- after the night's walking, I just couldn't-- couldn't-- couldn't walk any further.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
